plot: John Oliver examines food delivery apps' impact on restaurants, workers, and companies. He also discusses Donald Trump's Truth Social platform's stock performance versus its website traffic and popularity.

John Oliver discusses the unspoken sides of the food delivery apps, how it is hurting the restaurants, the delivery workers and even the app companies. He also talks Donald Trump's social media site Truth Social which is doing exceptionally good in the stocks but doing equally bad in website traffic and popularity.—Niaz Islam Arif
